If you're a gun aficionado or just a casual fan, this show should be interesting to you.  Shooting experts and ordinary people are included on the teams which compete until only one person remains who will win the title of Top Shot and a sizable cash prize.  The weapons include other guns from many eras and other weapons such as bow and arrows and even rocks, so the competition is not limited to just who is the best pistol or rifle shot.  Most of the time, it is hard to believe that an hour has passed when watching this show.  I believe it is currently in season six so this is a good way to catch up.  The only downside I know is sometimes the &#34;host&#34; talks a little too much.
